<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>168</hymn_number>
<title>A MAN A SUNG CH168</title>
<key>A</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kan lungthin Bawipa Biakinn thiang a si tikah, A chungah Bawipa a um,
 Thlacamnak thiang he a min in kan i pum i, Zeitluk in dah kan i lawmh.

[C1]
   A zummi hna caah cun a sunglawi bik, A cohlangmi hna caah a sunglawi
   bik; A min in kan i pum i, thluachuahnak kan hal lioah, Kan thlacamnak a
   cohlan.

[V2]
 A sunparnak chungin ceunak phun tling a tum, Kan ruahchannak zor hmanh
 seh, A dawtnak a ngan ruangah teinak kan hmuh lai, Amah he kan um ca ah.

[C2]
   A zummi hna caah cun a sunglawi bik, A cohlangmi hna caah a sunglawi
   bik; A min in kan i pum i, thluachuahnak kan hal lioah, Kan thlacamnak a
   cohlan.

[V3]
 A kan hruainak kan zulh i kan hna a ngamter, Kan chungah lawmhnak a
 khat, A hmunmi a kut in a kan huhphenh zungzal, ti cu fiang tein kan zumh.

[C3]
   A zummi hna caah cun a sunglawi bik, A cohlangmi hna caah a sunglawi
   bik; A min in kan i pum i, thluachuahnak kan hal lioah, Kan thlacamnak a
   cohlan.

[V4]
 Biatak hngalhnak in a vel chungah thang u si, Hnangamnak tling ngei u
 si. Siangpahrang inn ah zatial tlaih in kan leng lai, Lawmhnak a dong ti
 lai lo.

[C4]
   A zummi hna caah cun a sunglawi bik, A cohlangmi hna caah a sunglawi
   bik; A min in kan i pum i, thluachuahnak kan hal lioah, Kan thlacamnak a
   cohlan.</lyrics>
</song>